      • get

        public org.thymeleaf.TemplateEngine get()
        从接口复制的说明: TemplateEngineProvider
        Returns the TemplateEngine to use to render a Thymeleaf template. This method will be called repeatedly, so implementations should create the actual TemplateEngine object outside of this method. For an example, refer to DefaultTemplateEngineProvider.
        指定者:
        get 在接口中 TemplateEngineProvider
        返回:
        The TemplateEngine to use to render a Thymeleaf template.
